Wow!!! They remodeled and it looks and smells 100% better. 
They have a kios where you can order your food or you can have a staff at the counter do it. No waiting at counter for food. They give you a number you find a table and they deliver. 
The kids play area is much bigger. Clean and padded seats. The nicest play land ive been in!!

They really did a great job remodeling.